name: Verify Total Working Days tooltip

testSteps.description: 1: Verify Total Working Days tooltip ({parentTab=Leave Management, childTab=Apply, defaultTab=Leave, fromDate=21/10/2022, toDate=21/10/2022, heading=Apply Leave / WFH / Comp Off / Out Duty / Change Request})

children.description: Given User is logged into MIS
When User is on MIS Home Page
When User clicks on "Apply" sub tab of "Leave Management" tab
Navigate to sub tab: Apply, Leave Management
And Verify "Apply Leave / WFH / Comp Off / Out Duty / Change Request" of "Apply" tab
Verify tab displays: Apply Leave / WFH / Comp Off / Out Duty / Change Request
Then Select "21/10/2022" From date and "21/10/2022" till Leave dates from Calendar
Then Click on "Total Working Days" info icon
